==English==
===Noun===
'''epicycloid''' (''plural'' '''epicycloids''')
{{wikipedia}}
#{{geometry}} The [[locus]] of a [[point]] on the circumference of a [[circle]] that [[roll]]s without slipping on the circumference of another circle.

